      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "走吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00002",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内梆子导板",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我师傅在前途对我言，",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00003",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00004",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梆子原板",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "他叫我猪八戒前去探山。一路上看不尽花明柳暗，在山头看不了万顷良田。走一山又一山，山山相映，走一岭又一岭，岭岭相连。转过了小山坡用目观看，又只见山岗下一带清泉。",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00005",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我，猪八老爷的便是。我师徒四人去往西天取经。一路上，砖头也是怪，瓦块也是精，也不知道遇见了多少妖魔鬼怪。今儿个师傅又叫我去探山。这一路山清水秀，哪里会有妖精？这全是我猴儿哥的坏。我不免回去见了师傅，我就说：探着妖怪的下落啦！师傅要问我什么山，我就说是青石山；要问我是什么洞，我就说是白石洞；要问我是什么门，我就是说钉钉铁叶门；要问我见着妖精了没有，我就说是看见啦；要问我妖怪是什么样儿，我就说是青脸红发、巨齿獠牙、紫花屁股沟、酱色鸡巴毛。我就是这个主意。走吓！",
      "text_length": 230
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00006",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒学唱青衣。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00007",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "昔日里有一个孟姜女，他与那范郎送寒衣。哭倒了长城十数里，至今留名万古题。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00008",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "来此有户人家。待我看来。嘿嘿，这个地方。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00009",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "金铃大仙上，坐。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00010",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "有这么大的房子。呵，还有个小娘儿们。待我上前格搭格搭她。我说大嫂子请啦！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00011",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你是个做什么的？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00012",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我是个行路的。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00013",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你既行路，你只管在这里看什么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00014",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我看你长得好看。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00015",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "那么你就看。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00016",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我就看看看。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00017",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "小曲",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "四月里四月二十八，娘娘庙里把香插。打南来了个小大姐，年纪不过刚二八：梳油头，打云鬓，漆黑的头发红头绳儿扎。苏州的香粉扑满面，扬州的胭脂把脸蛋儿搽。两道弯眉如柳叶，樱桃小口一点点大。三寸金莲窄又瘦，走一步，咯答答。我要上前拉她一把，她可不住地叫她妈。",
      "text_length": 124
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00018",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你唱完了没有？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00019",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我唱完了，还没尽兴，我还要再乐一个。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00020",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你还唱什么呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00021",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "你听了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00022",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "京调",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "一更里进绣兰房，樱桃口呼唤声梅香：你把那个银灯儿拿上，对菱花卸去残妆，泪两行。叫丫鬟，你把那个门，门关上，听谯楼更鼓凄忙。入罗帷懒脱衣裳，细思量，一纱窗月影，月照窗，窗棂上。",
      "text_length": 87
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00023",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "你听好不好？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00024",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "好。你再唱一出。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00025",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "再唱一出？你倒听出了瘾来啦！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00026",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "玉美情人",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "玉美呀情人病在床，叫了声冤家，快进奴的房，有话与你商量。手拉手儿床沿坐，低声悄语叫了声哥哥，你稳坐听奴家说：从前嘎得病盼望着好，如今晚的病儿重加十分，要见五殿阎君。这是吓，银子三百两，拿回家去娶上门子亲，传留后代根。娶妻吓，必要坐家女，莫娶烟花柳巷人。如今晚的姑娘没有良心，一派地假殷勤，米汤可就灌死了人。",
      "text_length": 153
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00027",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我唱了这么半天，连一碗水都没有喝。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00028",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "那么你就请进来坐坐，我与你去倒茶去。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00029",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "好好好，我就到你里头去。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00030",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "什么？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00031",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "我到里头去坐坐。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00032",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "金铃大仙"
      ],
      "text": "你等着，我去与你倒茶去。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00033",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "金铃大仙下。猪八戒看。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00034",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "这是个石头洞吓。这桌子上霞光万道，瑞气千条，这是什么东西？哎呀，敢自我到了妖怪家里来了。这不是魂铃么？待我偷了去，我趁着没人，我快逃走了吧。",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00035",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒下。四小妖、二妖怪同追下。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00036",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒上，妖怪追上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00037",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妖怪"
      ],
      "text": "呔！你是何人？擅敢盗俺的宝贝。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00038",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "你休得胡言，宝铃取你。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00039",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒摇铃，妖怪笑。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00040",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "怎么不响吓？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00041",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "妖怪摇铃。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00042",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妖怪"
      ],
      "text": "看宝铃。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00043",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒下，众人追下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00044",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "辞别师傅下山林，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00045",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空上，耍棍。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00046",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "八戒前去盗魂铃。迈步转过高峰岭，人声呐喊为何情？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00047",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "我命八戒去盗魂铃，这般时候不见到来，也不知何处呐喊，待俺空中一望。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00048",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空上桌，猪八戒上，妖怪、众小妖同追上，开打，猪八戒下，众人同追下。孙悟空下桌。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00049",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "果然是八戒与众妖魔争斗起来。待我拔些毫毛，变些子子孙孙与妖魔交战便了。哧。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00050",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四小猴执棍同上，教演，转场。众小妖、妖怪同上，起打。妖怪下。小猴童耍棍，拉下场，同下。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00051",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00052",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "看我猴儿哥，带了许多猴儿崽子，杀得十分热闹。我不免也下上几个小猪，同他去打。待我养来。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00053",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小猪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00054",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，屙出一个来啦。等我到这边来，再下上一个。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00055",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小猪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00056",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "又一个，再来一个。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00057",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小猪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00058",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "又是一个，还少一个。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00059",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小猪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00060",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "屙的屁股眼疼。等我坎钏子坎一罢。够了够了。待我教与你。来，给你一根耙子，给你一根，再给你们两个人两根。来，跟着我走。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00061",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒、四小猪同跑大圆场三次。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00062",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "text": "立正！开步走！向右转！立正！开步走！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015009_e00063",
      "play_id": "01015009",
      "scene_id": "01015009_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪八戒、四小猪同下。众妖怪同上，起打。众人群场，十二股荡八连环，打，同下。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
